Doggy

00:09:07.458 --> 00:09:08.625
Second Brother

00:09:09.000 --> 00:09:10.458
You and Elder Brother

00:09:10.833 --> 00:09:12.708
Stop fighting

00:09:13.958 --> 00:09:14.750
I

00:09:15.666 --> 00:09:17.041
I'm scared

00:09:19.208 --> 00:09:20.375
Doggy

00:09:27.875 --> 00:09:29.875
All soldiers, listen up

00:09:31.916 --> 00:09:35.083
We once swore an oath

00:09:36.000 --> 00:09:37.708
Not to fail our country

00:09:38.000 --> 00:09:39.583
Not to fail our people

00:09:39.666 --> 00:09:41.125
Fight for our nation

00:09:41.208 --> 00:09:43.166
Die on the battlefield

00:09:44.208 --> 00:09:45.208
Now

00:09:46.625 --> 00:09:50.250
If we cross the boundary between the living and the dead

00:09:51.125 --> 00:09:54.833
We will end up harming the people

00:09:55.333 --> 00:09:58.625
Is this what we should do?

00:09:59.083 --> 00:10:00.750
No, we shouldn't

00:10:00.750 --> 00:10:04.208
Soldiers, don't forget our oath

00:10:04.750 --> 00:10:06.708
Protect the nation and fight the enemy

00:10:11.791 --> 00:10:13.166
Now

00:10:15.291 --> 00:10:16.791
We ourselves

00:10:18.208 --> 00:10:20.791
have become the enemies of our own people

00:10:29.875 --> 00:10:31.125
Brothers

00:10:32.125 --> 00:10:33.500
For the last time

00:10:34.791 --> 00:10:37.500
I'll lead you to protect the nation and fight

00:10:38.583 --> 00:10:40.416
Heaven and Earth

