00:12:18.375 --> 00:12:19.500
Are you sure

00:12:19.625 --> 00:12:21.583
that the dragon vein where soldiers are sacrificed

00:12:22.083 --> 00:12:24.458
is actually changing the feng shui of the Tang royal family?

00:12:25.333 --> 00:12:26.000
Yes

00:12:26.250 --> 00:12:27.666
From my observation

00:12:27.833 --> 00:12:30.000
They're not using human sacrifice to restore the dragon vein

00:12:30.208 --> 00:12:32.291
They're completely overturning and replacing it

00:12:33.125 --> 00:12:34.750
It seems someone powerful in the court

00:12:34.875 --> 00:12:37.500
wants to use feng shui art to seize the throne

00:12:38.833 --> 00:12:41.666
Sun, the magistrate of Fuping County, presented the Chapter of Ruling the Country

00:12:41.708 --> 00:12:43.583
to a high-ranking official in the capital

00:12:43.833 --> 00:12:44.750
In Luoyang

00:12:44.791 --> 00:12:47.625
another high official is using Liuxiang Pavilion to control officials

00:12:48.458 --> 00:12:51.500
